&lt;p&gt;一个有趣的例子 belike：&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;img data-src=&#34;https://quasdo.oss-cn-hangzhou.aliyuncs.com/img/image-20230616142349234.png&#34; alt=&#34;image-20230616142349234&#34; /&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
